subject: Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Rutgers was the tournament’s defending champion, but the Scarlet Knights were eliminated by seventh-seeded Louisville on a basket by Candyce Bingham with 32.8 seconds left.
